    "Such sources retain a placeholder-value of exactly zero for the PSF moments (among other parameters), and are therefore able to be removed by selecting only galaxies with (PSF_Q11 ̸ = 0.0) and (PSF_Q22 ̸ = 0.0).",
    "(32)This causes a significant reduction of the sample, removing over 20 million sources.",
